Also happens on nightly and for other "flattened" iterators. For example, Bevy's [QueryIter](https://docs.rs/bevy_ecs/0.9.0/bevy_ecs/query/struct.QueryIter.html) and [Query::for_each](https://docs.rs/bevy_ecs/0.9.0/bevy_ecs/query/struct.QueryState.html#method.for_each) show this exact API split due to this performance difference.

There seems to be #87411 that was targeting something similar.
